At the bottom of the valley is the smell of murder.

5
00:00:26,640 --> 00:00:28,140
He sees through the one and only truth.

6
00:00:28,140 --> 00:00:30,140
A child in appearance with the I.Q. of an adult.

7
00:00:30,140 --> 00:00:32,540
His name is Detective Conan.

8
00:01:53,199 --> 00:01:56,999
"Mt. Ryujin in West Tama County"

9
00:01:57,199 --> 00:02:00,999
"Tsuzura Ori Pass"

10
00:02:02,199 --> 00:02:04,299
Some hill this is!

11
00:02:04,299 --> 00:02:06,799
We've come so far up.

12
00:02:06,799 --> 00:02:08,999
We've still got a long way to go.

13
00:02:08,999 --> 00:02:11,599
We've only come about halfway.

14
00:02:11,599 --> 00:02:14,599
Oh, no. You've gotta be kidding.

15
00:02:14,599 --> 00:02:16,299
What's up?

16
00:02:16,299 --> 00:02:17,899
Oh, man.

17
00:02:17,899 --> 00:02:20,599
With all that right and left swinging,

18
00:02:20,599 --> 00:02:22,599
